These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, pineapple, raspberry, kale
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, card-games, reading, magic-tricks
House: art-deco, cape-cod, tower, palace
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola, milk, soy-milk
 1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the tower house##3
 2. the tower house is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 3. the person eating cherry is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the palace house is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 5. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 6. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
 7. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1
 8. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
 9. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
10. the palace house is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the person eating cherry##7
11. the palace house is on the right of the tower house##1
12. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
13. the person drinking soy-milk is the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food   | kale    | pineapple | raspberry    | cherry   |
| Hobby   | dancing | reading | card-games | magic-tricks |
| House           | cape-cod       | tower   | palace  | art-deco     |
| Beverage     | fanta      | milk   | soy-milk    | cola    |

