.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, january, november, july
4 different pets are kept: lizard, pony, rabbit, hedgehog
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, board-games, writing, camping
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, folk, d&b, indie
 1. the fan indie is somewhere to the left of the fan folk##5
 2. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 3. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
 4. the fan d&b is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 5. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
 6. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##5
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere between the fan folk and the person who's hobby is fishing##7
 8. the person who's birthday is in august is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the left of the fan folk##5
10. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the fan trance##5
11. the person who's hobby is board-games is the fan indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| Birthday          | august   | november       | july    | january      |
| Pet   | lizard | hedgehog | pony         | rabbit   |
| Hobby   | camping   | fishing  | board-games       | writing |
| Music-Genre         | trance      | d&b  | indie | folk |

