.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, baseball, soccer, rugby
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, rock, jazz, salsa
4 different games are played: snooker, backgammon, poker, monopoly
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, fonseca, pall-mall, cain
 1. the cain-smoker is somewhere to the left of the fan jazz##5
 2. the cain-smoker is somewhere between the person who's sport is water-polo and the fan jazz##7
 3. the person who's sport is baseball is the person playing backgammon##1
 4. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
 5. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the fan salsa##3
 6. the bluemaster-smoker is somewhere to the right of the fan ambient##5
 7. the person who's sport is soccer is not the fan rock##6
 8. the fan jazz is not the person who's sport is rugby##6
 9. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the fan rock##3
10. the cain-smoker is on the right of the fan salsa##1
11. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the fan jazz##3
12. the person playing poker is the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
| Sport           | rugby | water-polo | baseball | soccer |
| Music-Genre   | ambient        | salsa    | rock    | jazz    |
| Game   | snooker        | monopoly   | backgammon   | poker         |
| Cigar           | fonseca          | bluemaster       | cain   | pall-mall           |

