 7. the indian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere between the indian and the dutch##7
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is the person playing mah-jongg##1
10. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
11. the person who's birthday is in august is not the person playing mah-jongg##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |        3        |      4       |
| Food      | garlic | tomato       | peach         | cauliflower       |
