 2. the designer is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 3. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the videographer##5
 4. the scientist is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 5. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5
 6. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the writer##3
 7. the person playing whist is somewhere between the person who likes grey and the person who likes yellow##7
 8. the person playing go is not the person who likes grey##6
 9. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
10. the farmhouse house is on the left of the scientist##1
11. the wooden house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
12. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Game         | domino      | whist   | go   | canasta       |
| House   | ranch-style | farmhouse    | craftsman | wooden       |
| Job   | designer  | writer | scientist   | videographer     |
| Color         | grey   | fuchsia    | yellow   | ivory |

