.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, cain, bongani, bolivar
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, may, march, june
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, bellflower, azalea, iris
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, tea, hot-chocolate, cola
 1. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
 2. the person who's birthday is in march is the bongani-smoker##1
 3. the person drinking tea is the person who growsiris##1
 4. the person who growsazalea is between the bolivar-smoker and the cain-smoker##2
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the cain-smoker##5
 6. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in march and the swisher-smoker##7
 7. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
 8. the person who growsmarigold is the person drinking lemonade##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
10. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
12. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the cain-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
